# Dr. Data branding

Use these tokens everywhere. No generic grays as primary surfaces; no default system fonts for headings.

## Colors

- **Navy** `#1E2A3A` — text, primary buttons, headers
- **Teal** `#2DD4BF` — accents, selected states, secondary CTAs
- **Coral** `#F87171` — alerts, delete/warning actions, errors
- **Cream** `#F5EDD8` — page background

## Typography

- **Headings / display:** Space Grotesk (`font-display`)
- **Body:** Inter (`font-sans`)

Load from Google Fonts: Inter + Space Grotesk.

## Layout

- Mobile-first. Minimum **16px** font size on inputs. Minimum **48px** touch targets on buttons and primary inputs.
- No hover-only affordances; active/focus states must work on touch.

